, processes, stores and analyzes petabytes of interesting telemetry data excite you? We\u2019re looking for you! Are you an experienced Software Engineering Manager? In this role you\u2019ll both set direction and provide mentorship to our experienced engineers and work hands-on to solve sophisticated problems from the device level all the way to big data scale. You\u2019ll be responsible for the development, quality and integrity of the data pipelines which deliver a diverse set of data types to other engineering teams at apple.\n\nIn this role you\u2019ll have a large impact on the entire Apple Software Engineering organization and ultimately help Apple improve, build and deliver the products which consistently delight our users.\n\nEducation & Experience\n\nB.S. in Computer Science or equivalent experience\n\nAdditional Requirements\n\u2022 Expert level experience with Data Engineering tools and frameworks, processes, goals and methodologies.\n\u2022 Expert level experience with at least two of the following languages and related development tools: (Python, Ruby, Java, Scala, Swift, Objective C).\n\u2022 Experience with one or more of the following platforms: HDFS, Yarn, Spark, Impala, Kafka, HBase, MapReduce, Kubernetes, Object Store, Flink"
